'''飓风埃尔南'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Hernan}}）是[[2002年太平洋飓风季|2002年太平洋飓风季]]共计3场[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]中的第2场，也是该季第12个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，第10个获命名的风暴和第6场飓风。系统源于从大西洋进入太平洋的一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，催生出[[低气压|低气压]]系统后于8月30日组织成热带低气压{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带低气压是指[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]在每小时62公里以下的热带气旋<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，再于8月31日成为热带风暴{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的热带气旋<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，当晚达到飓风标准。{{#tag:ref|根据[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的定义，飓风是指持续风速在每小时119公里或以上的[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋]]和东北太平洋[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，这一标准同西北太平洋的[[台风|台风]]相同<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Miles B. Lawrence | title = Hurricane Hernan Tropical Cyclone Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022172456/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002hernan.shtml | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-10-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002hernan.shtml | archivedate = 2013-10-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>埃尔南迅速强化，最高强度达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的五级飓风标准。气旋向西北方向移动，在最高强度下保持了8个小时。9月2日，飓风因进入海域[[海面温度|水温]]降低而开始减弱。到9月6日时，系统已退化成残留低气压区。<ref name="tcr" />

埃尔南是本季第二强烈的飓风，并且在五级强度下持续的时间也是第二长，两项数据都仅次于[[2002年飓风肯纳|飓风肯纳]]<ref name="EPAC HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | date = 2014-07-07 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = The Northeast and North Central Pacific hurricane database 1949–2013 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-nencpac-1949-2013-070714.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140912211312/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-nencpac-1949-2013-070714.txt | archivedate = 2014-09-12 | deadurl = no }} A guide on how to read the database is available [http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tracks-hurdat2-epac-format-apr13.pdf here] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tracks-hurdat2-epac-format-apr13.pdf |date=20150923190243 }}.</ref>。风暴始终远离陆地，但4至6米高的涌浪还是令[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]沿岸出现轻度海滩[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]。此外，气旋的残留水分经过[[南加州|南加州]]近海，给当地带去少量降水<ref name="rain">{{cite newspaper | title = Showers along the Southwest coast | year = 2002 | newspaper = ''Syracuse Post-Standard''}}</ref>。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Hernan 2002 track.png}}
8月16日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲海岸。系统向西穿越[[大西洋|大西洋]]，行经[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]，与[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]中存在的一股[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]融合。系统逐渐发展出中等强度[[对流|对流]]，到8月30日时已有显著发展，成为第十{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。<ref name="tcr" />低气压继续产生强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]，并且主要集中在[[环流|环流]]中心以西和东北两侧的深层对流区内<ref name="tcr" />。虽然中心呈现不规则的拉长，但系统上空的[[风切变|风切变]]一直很少，[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]格局也很有利，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此预计气旋会适度增强<ref name="disc 2">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004925/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.002.html | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Depression 10-E Discussion Number 2 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.002.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。8月30日下午，低气压已发展出明显的[[雨带|带状特征]]，随即升级成热带风暴并获名“埃尔南”（{{lang|en|Hernan}}），风力时速72公里<ref name="PAN 3">{{cite web | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Hernan Public Advisory Number 3 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.003.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004939/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.003.html }}</ref>。气旋继续组织<ref name="PAN 3" />，环流中心由雷暴对流带围绕<ref name="disc3">{{cite web | author = Beven | title = Tropical Storm Hernan Public Advisory Number 4 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021004952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.004.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.004.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。8月31日，埃尔南在行进至[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]西南方向约634公里海域时升级成飓风<ref name="disc4">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 5 | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005009/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.005.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.005.html }}</ref>。
[[Image:Hurricane_Hernan_(2002)_TRMM.JPG|200px]]

由于风切变少、[[海面温度|海面温度]]高，风暴继续稳步增强，卫星图像显示8月31日晚系统中已发展出[[风眼|风眼]]<ref name="disc5">{{cite web | author = Avila | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 6 | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005117/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.006.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.006.html }}</ref>。埃尔南的最低[[气压|气压]]降至987[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]），[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]提高到每小时160公里<ref name="disc5" />，属[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准。风暴很快达到三级飓风强度，成为大型飓风{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中达到三级或以上的风暴<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr" />，不久后又成为四级飓风。与此同时，埃尔南的风眼变得模糊<ref name="disc6">{{cite web | author = Jarvinen/Knabb | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 8 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005130/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.008.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.008.html }}</ref>，并沿美国上空的强烈上层[[高压脊|高压脊]]南部边缘朝西北方向移动，横向移动速度增至每小时约27公里<ref name="disc6" />。到了9月1日，飓风达到风力时速260公里，最低气压921毫巴（百帕）的最高强度，属五级飓风标准<ref name="tcr" />，也是[[2002年太平洋飓风季|2002年太平洋飓风季]]3场五级飓风中的第2场<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。

9月2日，风暴的对流雷暴带温度略有上升，表明气旋强度降至略低于五级飓风标准<ref name="tcr" />。埃尔南进入[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]周期，形成双层风眼墙<ref name="disc7">{{cite web | author = Jarvinen/Molleda | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 12 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005157/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.012.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.012.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>并继续减弱，其强度于当天降至三级飓风水平，之后很快就略朝西面转向<ref name="disc8">{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 14 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.014.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005211/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.014.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。埃尔南接下来进入又一轮眼墙置换周期，风速进一步减慢<ref name="disc9">{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 15 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005221/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.015.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.015.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。由于风暴进入的海域水温降低，其风速也降至每小时160公里以下，低于大型飓风标准<ref name="tcr" />。不久后，埃尔南降级成一级飓风，风眼被云层阻挡<ref name="disc10">{{cite web | author = Avila | title = Hurricane Hernan Public Advisory Number 19 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005246/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.019.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.019.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。9月5日，气旋虽然发展出新的对流带，但风力时速却急剧下降至72公里<ref name="disc12">{{cite web | author = Stewart/Rhome | title = Tropical Storm Hernan Public Advisory Number 25 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005326/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.025.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.025.html }}</ref>，进一步降级成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" />。同日，风暴退化成热带低气压，并开始失去热带天气系统特征<ref name="tcr" />。受强烈的风切变影响，低气压进一步消亡<ref name="disc13">{{cite web | author = Stewart/Rhome | title = Tropical Depression Hernan Public Advisory Number 29 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005339/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.029.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/ep102002.discus.029.html | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。9月6日，埃尔南退化成残留[[低气压|低气压系统]]<ref name="tcr" />，其残留水分沿[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]海岸蜿蜒行进，产生少量降水<ref name="tcr" />。

== 影响和纪录 ==
飓风埃尔南自始至终远离海岸，没有对陆地构成显著影响<ref name="tcr" />。墨西哥近海的[[索科罗岛|索科罗岛]]出现微风，大浪造成轻度影响。飓风中心所在开放海域附近产生的巨浪估计有21米高，但这一数据没有得到正式报告确认。气象机构的浮标测得高达17米的涌浪。<ref name="surf">{{cite web | author = Nathan Todd Cool | title = 70 waves generated by Hernan | publisher = WaveCast | accessdate = 2015-06-27 | url = http://wavecast.com/guide/questions.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210170258/http://wavecast.com/guide/questions.shtml | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>墨西哥沿海的浪高有4到6米，引发轻度海滩[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]<ref name="ncdc">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | title = Event Report for Hurricane Hernan | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2012-01-13 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~450914 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120113014147/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~450914 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-01-13 | date =  }}</ref>。风暴的部分残留水分在[[南加州|南加州]]沿岸行进期间产生小雨，导致道路湿滑，但没有任何报道表明气旋有对海上船只构成影响<ref name="rain" />。

埃尔南从热带风暴增强成五级飓风期间的气压下降速度为每小时1.73毫巴（百帕），低于“[[快速增强|快速增强]]”的标准。但从8月31日至9月1日的12小时里，其气压每小时下降了2.58毫巴，属“爆发性增强”，这主要是因为风暴当时所处环境风切变少，海面温度也比较高<ref name="weather">{{cite web | author = Gary Padgett | title = August Tropical Cyclone Summary | accessdate = 2008-02-20 | url = http://www.weathermatrix.net/archive/tropical/summaries-2002/0012.html | publisher = Weathermatrix | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2005-11-27 | date = 2002-10-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20051127172419/http://www.weathermatrix.net/archive/tropical/summaries-2002/0012.html }}</ref>。

